Thousands of years ago the Chinese discovered that many meridians either commence
or terminate on the face and some have internal branches that go to the face,
correlating the relationship of health and appearance. Changes and deterioration
in the skin, muscle tone, and sense organs reflect the state of thezang fu, qi,
blood, yin and yang.<br>
